project_descr: In line with the mid term evaluation of the Phase 1 of the Fiji Parliament Support Project, Phase 2 will focus on further institutional development of the Parliament and accompanying it through the 2018 elections transition period.

outputs.output_descr: The project  provides MPs and staff with enhanced institutional and capacity development strengthening.  Parliament has limited capacities to discharge its mandate in relation to legislation, oversight and representation.
donor_name: NEW ZEALAND AGY FOR INT'L DEVE
